# Base agent needs no secrets for local tools (JSON under var/).
#
# Connections use Vercel Connect (app-scoped) unless noted:
#   vercel link
#   vercel connect create <service>
#   vercel env pull
#
# Channel-specific env (if you enable that channel):
#   Slack — via Connect
#   Discord — DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN, DISCORD_PUBLIC_KEY
#   Telegram — TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN
#   GitHub App — GITHUB_APP_ID, GITHUB_APP_PRIVATE_KEY, GITHUB_WEBHOOK_SECRET
#   Browser Use — BROWSER_USE_API_KEY
#
# Model access follows your eve setup (Vercel AI Gateway or a provider key).
